女心善手软，我让她打回去她当时不敢）"},"attached_info":"Cj8IosPaqrOx6uRkEAMaCDk2MjY3MzY4IIvru6MGMAg46wFADHIJNjAyOTQxNTQ5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"9 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a3dfa6daf74d1ff46701931b73fab444_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1685877165.0164614","card_id":"Q_603935230","target":{"id":603935230,"title":"为何郑州与长沙的地铁客流量差距这么大？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/603935230","type":"question","created":1685457959,"answer_count":54,"follower_count":120,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[309,1717,2071,2464,100973],"comment_count":2,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"如下图，实际不仅仅是5月28日，长沙地铁人数长期以来一直都比郑州多出一个层级，一百万人。而客流强度一直都是郑州的一倍。 像西安，武汉，城区人口都将近1000万，郑州比不过很正常。然而长沙和郑州城区人口是差不多的，为什么地铁客流量差距如此巨大？ 这是何故？"},"attached_info":"ClQIosPaqrOx6uRkEAMaCDk2NDg4MDQ1IKeY2KMGMAI4eEANcgk2MDM5MzUyMzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I=","detail_text":"8 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-a1289a9e975be601182f164de845ee3e_1440w.webp"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"14_1685877165.017574","card_id":"Q_604444104","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":604444104,"title":"五月百城二手住宅均价环比下跌 0.25%，北京二手房成交量跌破 1.3 万套，六月楼市会怎么走？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/604444104","type":"question","created":1685700753,"answer_count":129,"follower_count":370,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1708,9220,14282,70742,1344154],"comment_count